reviewText: Interesting documentary. Used for school project.

Wished this series wasn't so expensive,at the time of buying this DVD, each DVD with 1 episode cost 20 dollars, which i thought was a bit too much since is an old series,i bought this Boston episode to complement a present for my husband who likes this series a lot,he watched once and completely forgot about it since it wasn't a very entertaining episode.thanks God i didn't purchase any more of these DVDs and instead used that money towards buying seasons of Law and Order.
